## Monorepo gitignore (root)

# dependencies
**/node_modules

# build outputs
**/.next
**/out
**/dist
**/build

# local data / artifacts
**/.data
**/artifacts
**/playwright-report
**/test-results

# env / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# OS
.DS_Store

# misc (not part of product)
resume.site/
fix-playwright-proxy.patch
